  main.index
    section#intro.strip.strip--brand
      .strip__inner
          h3.title A Blockchain Powered Comments System
          p.strip__content Finally is a comments system for your website that is powered by the #[a.content-link(href="https://steem.io") STEEM blockchain]. The STEEM blockchain is a unique piece of technology that allows content creators to receive a share of weekly token rewards.
          p.strip__content Finally is a competitor to the current status quo of comments sytems that are rife with tracking and advertisment. Finally aims to provide monetisation to blogs and foster discussions with the incentives the STEEM blockchain provides.

          a.button.is-small.is-light(href="/about") Learn More

    section#get-started.strip.strip--alt
      .strip__inner
          h3.title Get Started

          p.strip__content Finally provides both HTML embed code and a javascript library. The HTML embed can be easily added to any website while the Javascript library enables advanced options for developers.
          p.strip__content Finally uses #[a.content-link(href="https://steemconnect.com/") Steemconnect] to allow users to post and upvote content. Once authenticated users will not have to log in again when visiting other sites that also use Finally.

          p.strip__content The fastest way to embed any of your recent comment threads from Steemit.com, Busy.org or any STEEM based platform is to login to our dashboard where you can see a complete list of your recent posts. From the Dashboard you can generate the embed code for any post with one click.

          p
            a.button.is-small.is-dark(href="/get-started") More Details
            a.button.is-small.is-dark(href="/auth/dashboard") Login With Steemconnect

